  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions and garlic and sauté until the onions are translucent.",
    "Add the pork and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the water, tamarind paste, fish sauce, soy sauce, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 1.5 hours, or until the pork is tender.",
    "Add the long green chili peppers and finger chilies to the pot and simmer for another 30 minutes.",
    "Add the tomatoes and bok choy to the pot and simmer for another 10 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the sinigang hot, garnished with tamarind leaves if desired."
